de.codecentric.boot.admin.server.services

类 InstanceRegistry

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.codecentric.boot.admin.server.services.InstanceRegistry

  • public class InstanceRegistry
extends Object
    Registry for all application instances that should be managed/administrated by the Spring Boot Admin server. Backed by an InstanceRepository for persistence and an InstanceIdGenerator for id generation.
